    "description": "This very neat, move-in-ready apartment is situated in the popular Unigloed Apartment Complex in the well-established suburb of Môregloed.\r\n\r\nThe 2nd floor unit offers:\r\n* 1 spacious bedroom\r\n* 1 bathroom\r\n* Neat kitchen\r\n* Comfortable living area\r\n* Prepaid electricity\r\n* Lock-up garage\r\n\r\nThe complex features a communal garden, braai area, and guest parking, creating a pleasant and welcoming environment for residents and visitors. The complex also has a lift, providing convenient access to the upper floors.\r\n\r\nSecurity includes electric gates and a CCTV camera system for added peace of mind.\r\n\r\nConveniently located near shopping centres, schools, and churches, this apartment is perfectly positioned in a well-established area.\r\n\r\nIdeal for investors, first-time buyers, or those looking to scale down.",
