    "description": "Discover this immaculate, well-maintained townhouse, perfectly located in the sought-after Villarus Complex. Move-in ready and ideal for comfortable family living!\r\n\r\nDownstairs features:\r\nA beautiful, modern kitchen with ample cupboard space, perfect for any home chef. The home offers a spacious dining area and two inviting living areas, creating a warm and versatile living environment. Step outside to your private garden with a patio and built-in braai—perfect for entertaining. A guest toilet and private washing line add to the convenience.\r\n\r\nUpstairs offers:\r\nThree generously sized bedrooms and two bathrooms. The main bedroom boasts its own private balcony—ideal for relaxing and enjoying quiet moments.\r\n\r\nAdditional features:\r\nThe complex offers a communal swimming pool with braai facilities.\r\n\r\nThe property includes one lock-up garage and one undercover parking. Levies conveniently include garden services. Electricity is post-paid.\r\n\r\nThis is a fantastic opportunity to own a beautiful home in a well-maintained and secure complex.",
